comments: Gobert (UTA) establishes himself in a screening position in Rozier's (CHA) path and gives him room to avoid the contact on the pick.
Conley (UTA) momentarily places a resting hand on Rozier's (CHA) body and marginal contact occurs, which does not affect Rozier's SQBR on the drive.
During the rebound, McDaniels (CHA) and Mitchell (UTA) both make clean ball contact as they pursue the loose ball.
Bogdanovic (UTA) legally contests Rozier's (CHA) jump shot attempt.
McDaniels (CHA) makes contact with Mitchell's (UTA) arm, which affects his driving shot attempt.
During the rebound, Gobert (UTA) and McDaniels (CHA) engage and disengage and the contact is marginal.
McDaniels (CHA) moves into Conley (UTA) and makes contact with his body, which dislodges him to the ground.
Gobert (UTA) turns into and makes contact with Bridges' (CHA) body, which affects his driving shot attempt.
Ball (CHA) swipes down and makes contact with Mitchell's (UTA) arm, which affects his driving shot attempt.
O'Neale (UTA) extends his arm to Ball's (CHA) back and delivers contact, which affects Ball's SQBR during his drive.
Gobert (UTA) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Mitchell (UTA) maintains a legal guarding position on Bridges (CHA) during the drive.
Gobert (UTA) collapses his forearm in to absorb the marginal contact on his contest during Bridges' (CHA) driving shot attempt.
Ball (CHA) reaches in and makes contact with Conley's (UTA) arm, which affects his SQBR.
